---
eleventyNavigation:
    key: "About"
    order: 2

title: About

roles: "UX / UI | Web Design | Frontend"
description: "Designer, Developer, Dilligent-worker. Adept at creating design systems suitable for a variety of scope sizes. Experienced mainly in the finance and non-profit sectors."

---
<section class="centre" id="about-snippet">
    <div class="section-row">
        <div class="row-column text">
            <h2 style="text-align: center;">{{roles}}</h2>
            <p class="text-div">{{description}}</p>
            {% set testList = testimonials | shuffle %}
            {% for testimonial in testList.slice(0,1) %}
            <li class="card testimonial">
                <q>{{testimonial.testimonial}}</q>
                <div class="persona"><i class="ri-chat-2-fill"></i><p><b>{{testimonial.persona}}</b></p></div>
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class ="row-column image">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/800/800">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="centre" id="CV">
    {% for job in cv %}
    <div class="CV">
        <div class="heading">
            <div class="company-role">
                <h3>{{job.company}}</h3>
                <ul class="roles-list">
                    {% for role in job.roles %}
                    <li>{{role}}</li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="location">
                <p>{{job.location}}, {{job.timePeriod}}</p>
                <a class="btn-small primary" href="{{job.link}}">Visit</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="job-info">
            <div class="text-div">
                <ul>
                {% for point in job.bulletPoints %}
                    <li>{{point}}</li>
                {% endfor %}
                </ul>
                <div>
                    {% for project in job.projects %}
                    <a class="btn secondary" href="{{project.link}}">{{project.title}}</a>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row-column image job-image">
                <img class="image" src="{{'../assets/images/3rd-party-logos/' + job.logo}}" loading="lazy" alt="logo">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
</section>

<section class="centre" id="about-purpose">
    <div class="section-row image-right">
        <div class="row-column text">
            <h2>Our Purpose</h2>
            <p>
                This organisation was created to identify and support students who are unable to pay 
                for additional tutoring services to supplement their education, because of financial 
                restraints and burdens.<br><br>

                Our services are unique in that they are not restricted to the traditional metrics
                qualifying <b>'disadvantaged backgrounds'</b>, but will also include those who seem to be
                financially secure on paper, <b>but are unable to fund these needs in reality</b>. Opening
                these services to those who fall through the cracks will allow us to empower <b>all</b> students
                to receive the guidance and support their needs.<br><br>
                
                We conduct regular tutoring sessions charged based on the financial capabilities of each individual
                student. All monetary profits are <b>reinvested</b> to expand the range and quality of 
                services and also increase the number of free students tutored. It's important to 
                ensure the students who want to study are given the chance to, regardless of their
                financial situation.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class ="row-column image">
			<img src="../assets/images/about/Our-Purpose.webp" alt="A student and tutor talk to eachother, supported by a drawing of hands. The student has a drawing of a lightbulb above their head, indicating an idea.">
		</div>
    </div>
    
</section>

